==Description==
The '''Twisted Spoon''' is a type of [[Held Items|Held Item]] that can only be equipped to [[File:Psychic_Type_icon.png|30px]]Psychic type Pokémon.

==Details==
Raises the attack of the Pokémon holding the Item by 10%.

